{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_0154DdiwhvKA3ti6izaKNtMN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0117UWUHZCt9ASLxwJwegbBw","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git add -u && git add src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/durability_open_path.rs && git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\ntest(durability): AC-035a/b/c open-path corruption matrix\n\nAdd four-fixture matrix wiring each `CorruptionKind` to a deterministic\non-disk corruption: WAL sidecar with invalid header (new helper),\npage-0 magic flip (existing), interior b-tree byte flip (existing),\nand embedder-profile dimension = -1 (new helper).\n\nThe matrix exposed two AC-035b routing gaps in `Engine::open` that the\nprior single test (`ac_006_*` in `lifecycle_observability.rs`) did not\ncatch:\n\n  - Page-0 magic flip surfaced via `pragma journal_mode = WAL` which\n    routed it to `(WalReplayFailure, WalReplay)` instead of the\n    documented `(HeaderMalformed, HeaderProbe)` row.\n  - Page-1 b-tree byte flips trip during the WAL pragma for the same\n    reason, masking the `(SchemaInconsistent, SchemaProbe)` row.\n\nFix by ordering the open path so each `CorruptionKind` has its own\ndedicated probe step:\n\n    HeaderProbe     -> PRAGMA application_id            (file header)\n    SchemaProbe     -> SELECT COUNT(*) FROM sqlite_schema (b-tree)\n    WalReplay       -> WAL sidecar magic + page-size pre-check,\n                       then pragma journal_mode = WAL\n    EmbedderIdentity -> check_embedder_profile\n\nThe WAL sidecar pre-check is also a real reliability win: SQLite\notherwise silently discards a malformed WAL, losing committed frames;\nwe now refuse to open with `Corruption(WalReplayFailure)`.\n\nAC-035c (lock release + no fd / writer-thread residue) is linux-only\nand serialized via a static mutex so sibling tests in the same binary\ndo not race the `/proc/self/{fd,task}` introspection.\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit Sub-1"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4242,"cache_read_input_tokens":170050,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4242},"output_tokens":43,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"af81e32e-38ea-41b6-ab82-41ce4c91617f","uuid":"e24d09a2-db00-4a78-a615-046dae75c249"}
